{"tid":726731,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"做魚米嘅入一入嚟，有嘢想問","createTime":"2018-07-02T15:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T09:49:57.000Z","uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"562980b7e77ab4d612d1ff8f51e37454c584d5c9","tid":726731,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:43:44.000Z","msg":"話說夜晚去咗新都城間魚米食，諗住之前食過佢啲米線好食過譚仔就食佢啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問題就嚟啦，我屋企人唔食米線叫咗呢個豬扒菜飯，啲豬扒燶咗都唔緊要啦 最多搣開層皮食囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢未食，一聞個飯，就話好「叔」，我就問個侍應，搞咩咁「叔」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知個侍應話因為個飯係焗住所以啲「叔」味係正常，跟住我真係食一啖飯，陣「叔」味係直頭食唔到，陣味好似個電飯煲煲完飯放係度幾一先打開嚟洗個陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做魚米嘅巴絲打，係咪個飯真係有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://serving.photos.photobox.com/0131908567e0e9a30a42748bc9e66d5c73b8b99f498a43cf14f8f11064f6c1763302db82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fserving.photos.photobox.com%2F0131908567e0e9a30a42748bc9e66d5c73b8b99f498a43cf14f8f11064f6c1763302db82.jpg&h=042da63f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e372b0f9c85a872e20caa08f05b1d6d38aa5fc1f","tid":726731,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:45:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://serving.photos.photobox.com/0131908567e0e9a30a42748bc9e66d5c73b8b99f498a43cf14f8f11064f6c1763302db82.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fserving.photos.photobox.com%2F0131908567e0e9a30a42748bc9e66d5c73b8b99f498a43cf14f8f11064f6c1763302db82.jpg&d=wYJ3saCtSGZJu1oBX3652S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5992785f\" target=\"_blank\">https://serving.photos.photobox.com/0131908567e0e9a30a42748bc9e66d5c73b8b99f498a43cf14f8f11064f6c1763302db82.jpg</a><br />\n張圖唔知點解調轉咗 入去條link睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe30f9e0fa4687cc11d9eb534c8dbc677cdc24f","tid":726731,"uid":55691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:49:21.000Z","msg":"係大圍食過 湯底還好 特別杯檸茶沖得幾好飲<br />\n但服務真係唔掂 成日錯單 入位又亂<br />\n有次明明出面勁多人排緊隊 有啲人可以直份亂坐無人發現<br />\n跟著隔離格等咗成個鐘 點既主菜未到<br />\n到到食完曬好耐之後個小食先再到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72eb1ca5009ee315494bb0c8ec47d50a48d510c","tid":726731,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfe30f9e0fa4687cc11d9eb534c8dbc677cdc24f","tid":726731,"uid":55691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:49:21.000Z","msg":"係大圍食過 湯底還好 特別杯檸茶沖得幾好飲<br />\n但服務真係唔掂 成日錯單 入位又亂<br />\n有次明明出面勁多人排緊隊 有啲人可以直份亂坐無人發現<br />\n跟著隔離格等咗成個鐘 點既主菜未到<br />\n到到食完曬好耐之後個小食先再到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T09:49:57.000Z","msg":"啲服務態度真係好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}